!! cursors
! X11 looks for cursors on the directory $path/$theme/cursors.
!
! I put my cursors at $HOME/lib/cursors. There are two ways I can do
! that: I can set path to "$HOME" and theme to "lib", so X11 concats all
! three pieces to "$HOME/lib/cursors"; or I can set path to "$HOME/lib"
! and theme to the empty string.  Xterm seems to prefer the latter.
Xcursor.path:                           $HOME/lib
Xcursor.theme:                          ""

