!! Athena widgets
! Command:      Regular button (normally rectangular, but I set them as oval)
! MenuButton:   Button that spawns a menu, similar to Command
! Toggle:       Button that toggles
! Radio:        Button that toggles
! Grip:         Rectangle used to reposition objects (usually Paneds)
! Paned:        Resizeable container box widget
! Box:          Fixed-size container box widget?
! Form:         Automatic-size container box widget?
! Label:        String container
! SimpleMenu:   Menu
! ScrollBar:    Scroll bar
*shadowWidth:                           2
*shapeStyle:                            oval
*Command.highlightThickness:            1
*Command.background:                    WIDHVY
*MenuButton.background:                 WIDHVY
*Toggle.background:                     WIDHVY
*Radio.background:                      WIDHVY
*Grip.foreground:                       WIDHVY
